rules.description: Map right ctrl to hyper
Map hyper-tab to control-tab
Map hyper-c to up
Map hyper-t to down
Map hyper-h to left
Map hyper-n to right
Map h to left in Preview
Map l to right in Preview
Map j to down in Preview
Map k to up in Preview
Map keypad 7 to keypad 1 in emacs
Map keypad 8 to keypad 2 in emacs
Map keypad 9 to keypad 3 in emacs
Map keypad 1 to keypad 7 in emacs
Map keypad 2 to keypad 8 in emacs
Map keypad 3 to keypad 9 in emacs
Map ctrl+w to alt + backspace outside of emacs and alacritty
Map ctrl+h to backspace outside of emacs and alacritty
Change right shift to # if alone
Change left shift to $ if alone
Change left_control to control if pressed with other keys, to escape if pressed alone.
Change left_control to control if pressed with other keys, to escape if pressed alone.
Change caps_lock to control if pressed with other keys, to escape if pressed alone.
Post right_ctrl when return_or_enter is hold.
Post escape if left_control is pressed alone.
Post return_or_enter if right_control is pressed alone.
